ite/wordpress-search-enhanced/\" rel=\"bookmark\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"screen-reader-text\">巧用分词搜索插件增强 WordPress 搜索性能</span></a>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grve-post-media\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grve-media-inner grve-radius-none grve-shadow-none\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grve-background-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grve-bg-image lazyload\" data-bgset=\"https://staticfile.shephe.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/searching.jpg 1500w, https://staticfile.shephe.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/searching-900x675.jpg 900w\" data-sizes=\"auto\"></div>\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grve-post-date grve-h5 grve-heading-color\">\t\t\t<time datetime=\"2024-04-08T18:06:00+08:00\">\n\t\t\t\t04/08/2024\t\t\t</time>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grve-post-content\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"grve-post-title grve-heading-color grve-h3\" itemprop=\"headline\"><span>巧用分词搜索插件增强 WordPress 搜索性能</span></h2>\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>一直以来 WordPress 都有个问题，它的搜索功能采用了完全匹配的模式，很多时候都无法得到自己想要的结果，做得跟屎一样！举个例子，这里前不久发布了一篇文章说想给博客改名，搜索“博客改名”能精确命中该文，但如果没有安装分词插件增强 Wor…</p>\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t<a class=\"grve-read-more grve-link-text\" href=\"https://www.shephe.com/website/wordpress-search-enhanced/\"><span>查看全文</span>\t\t\t\t<svg width=\"40px\" height=\"16px\" viewBox=\"0 0 40 16\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<polygon class=\"grve-arrow-line\" points=\"0 7 38 7 38 9 0 9\"></polygon>\n\t\t\t\t\t<polygon class=\"grve-arrow-point\" points=\"31.3481912 0 40 8 31.3481912 16 30 14.5816219 37.1 8 30 1.41837809\"></polygon>\n\t\t\t\t</svg>\n\t\t\t</a>","link":"https://www.shephe.com/website/wordpress-search-enhanced/","retrieved":1712900671389}]}